pyhole - A modular IRC bot for Python developers.


Core Requirements

    - Python 2.5+
    - Eventlet


Plugin Requirements

    - IMDbPY
    - launchpadlib
    - pywapi
    - simplejson


Installation

    git clone git://github.com/jk0/pyhole.git
    cd pyhole
    cp pyhole.cfg.dist pyhole.cfg
    vi pyhole.cfg

    ./pyhole.py
